## Normalising CSS

Browsers have slightly different default styling.

We want an easy way to **normalise** the experience
of different users on different browsers.

For instance,
the [latest Chrome user agent stylesheet](https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/blink/+/master/Source/core/css/html.css)
is very similar, but not an exact match,
to the [latest Firefox user agent stylesheet](https://dxr.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/source/layout/style/res/html.css).

